-- Putin Grants French Actor Gerard Depardieu Russian Citizenship
-- B y   S t e p h e n   B i e r m a n
-- 2013-01-03T09:19:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-03/putin-grants-french-actor-gerard-depardieu-russian-citizenship.html
Russian President Vladimir Putin signed an order granting French actor Gerard Depardieu Russian citizenship, according to a statement posted on the Kremlin website today.  Depardieu is moving to Belgium to flee taxes imposed on the wealthy by Socialist President  Francois Hollande . A spokeswoman for the actor declined to comment.  To contact the reporter on this story: Stephen Bierman in Moscow at  sbierman1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story: Will Kennedy at  wkennedy3@bloomberg.net  